FlogHelper is a Fred plugin. It allows easy flogging (Freenet blogging)
using the FProxy interface (which means within a browser).

It's currently under developement.

Key features :
* Easy to use by newbies, secure
* WoT integration (for comments & author identity)
* Freetalk integration (for comments)
* Store flog data in node.db4o 

Todo list :
* Freetalk !
* Index generation / search form
